Class ImportController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.Controller
      • controllers.ImportController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class ImportController
extends Controller
    This class is used when User presses the "import" button in main calendar view. It tries to add as many events as it can without any overlapping issues, then, if there are any events still to add, creates an instance of ImportManager.
    See Also:
